交通运输.sqlite:
CREATE TABLE Passengers on rail transport (
  Year VARCHAR(50) PRIMARY KEY, -- 年份
  Railway operations mileage DATETIME, -- 铁路营业里程
  The mileage rises the same as the rest of the year INTEGER, -- 里程同比增长
  Iron mileage ratio INTEGER, -- 高铁里程占比
  Passengers ' dispatches INTEGER, -- 旅客发送量
  Traveler growth over time INTEGER, -- 旅客同比增长
  Portfolio turnover INTEGER, -- 客运周转量
  Growth in liquidity on a one-year basis INTEGER, -- 周转量同比增长
  High Iron Carrier Ratio INTEGER, -- 高铁承运占比
);
CREATE TABLE Goods transported by rail (
  Year INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, -- 年份
  Shipment volume DATETIME, -- 货运发送量
  Sends increase on the same basis INTEGER, -- 发送量同比增长
  Freight turnover INTEGER, -- 货运周转量
  Growth in liquidity on a one-year basis INTEGER, -- 周转量同比增长
);
CREATE TABLE Civil aviation routes (
  Year INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, -- 年份
  Number of civil aviation certified airports DATETIME, -- 民用航空颁证机场数量
  Number of regular air access airports INTEGER, -- 定期通航机场数量
  Number of navigable cities INTEGER, -- 通航城市数量
  Number of aircraft INTEGER, -- 飞机数量
  Course miles INTEGER, -- 航线里程
  Urban coverage at the local level INTEGER, -- 地级市覆盖率
  District coverage INTEGER, -- 县覆盖率
  Number of international routes INTEGER, -- 国际航线数量
  Number of shipping countries INTEGER, -- 通航国家数量
);
CREATE TABLE Passengers transported by civil aviation (
  Year INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, -- 年份
  Passenger traffic DATETIME, -- 旅客运输量
  Traveler growth over time INTEGER, -- 旅客同比增长
  Passenger turnover INTEGER, -- 旅客周转量
  Growth in liquidity on a one-year basis INTEGER, -- 周转量同比增长
);
CREATE TABLE Transport of goods by civil aviation (
  Year INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, -- 年份
  Postage traffic DATETIME, -- 货邮运输量
  Increase in volume of transport on a par INTEGER, -- 运输量同比增长
  Postage turnover INTEGER, -- 货邮周转量
  Growth in liquidity on a one-year basis INTEGER, -- 周转量同比增长
);

明星关系.sqlite:
CREATE TABLE Star (
  Phrase id VARCHAR(50) PRIMARY KEY, -- 词条id
  Name INTEGER, -- 姓名
  Age VARCHAR(50), -- 年龄
  Graduate schools INTEGER, -- 毕业院校
  Time of graduation VARCHAR(50), -- 毕业时间
);
CREATE TABLE Star couple (
  Starid DATETIME PRIMARY KEY, -- 明星id
  Spouse id INTEGER, -- 配偶id
  Time of marriage INTEGER, -- 结婚时间
  Number of children DATETIME, -- 子女数量
);
CREATE TABLE A divorcing star (
  Starid INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, -- 明星id
  Spouse id INTEGER, -- 配偶id
  Departure time INTEGER, -- 离异时间
  Number of children DATETIME, -- 子女数量
);
CREATE TABLE Starfriend (
  Starid INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, -- 明星id
  Friend id INTEGER, -- 好友id
  Relations INTEGER, -- 关系
);
